│[1m [0m[1mpatch_description       [0m[1m [0m│ Introduce a lightweight simulated annealing refinement inside the main packing            │
│[1m                          [0m│ construction to escape local optima and boost the total sum of radii. The SA operates on  │
│[1m                          [0m│ both centers and radii by perturbing a small subset of centers, recomputing feasible      │
│[1m                          [0m│ radii, and accepting improvements (or near-improvements) with a temperature-guided        │
│[1m                          [0m│ probability. This complements the existing multi-start initializations and the local      │
│[1m                          [0m│ optimizer, aiming to push the sum of radii beyond prior bests (target > 2.635). The       │
│[1m                          [0m│ refinement is implemented as a nested function inside construct_packing to avoid altering │
│[1m                          [0m│ the module-level API and to keep changes localized and reproducible.                      │
